# Code-Hex/vz v3 Complete API Reference

## 1. VirtualMachineConfiguration

`VirtualMachineConfiguration` is the core configuration object for creating virtual machines.

### Constructor
```go
func NewVirtualMachineConfiguration(bootLoader BootLoader, cpu uint, memorySize uint64) (*VirtualMachineConfiguration, error)
```

### Key Methods

| Method | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `Validate()` | Validates the configuration before VM creation |
| `NetworkDevices()` | Returns configured network devices |
| `StorageDevices()` | Returns configured storage devices |
| `SocketDevices()` | Returns configured socket devices |
| `USBControllers()` | Returns configured USB controllers |

### Configuration Setters
```go
// Network configuration
SetNetworkDevicesVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []*VirtioNetworkDeviceConfiguration)

// Storage configuration
SetStorageDevicesVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []StorageDeviceConfiguration)

// Socket configuration
SetSocketDevicesVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []SocketDeviceConfiguration)

// Directory sharing
SetDirectorySharingDevicesVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []DirectorySharingDeviceConfiguration)

// Peripherals
SetKeyboardsVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []KeyboardConfiguration)
SetPointingDevicesVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []PointingDeviceConfiguration)
SetSerialPortsVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []*VirtioConsoleDeviceSerialPortConfiguration)

// Audio/Graphics
SetAudioDevicesVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []AudioDeviceConfiguration)
SetGraphicsDevicesVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []GraphicsDeviceConfiguration)
SetConsoleDevicesVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []ConsoleDeviceConfiguration)

// Advanced
SetEntropyDevicesVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []*VirtioEntropyDeviceConfiguration)
SetMemoryBalloonDevicesVirtualMachineConfiguration(cs []MemoryBalloonDeviceConfiguration)
SetUSBControllersVirtualMachineConfiguration(us []USBControllerConfiguration)
SetPlatformVirtualMachineConfiguration(c PlatformConfiguration)
```

### Example Configuration
```go
config, err := vz.NewVirtualMachineConfiguration(
    bootLoader,  // BootLoader interface
    4,           // CPU count
    8589934592,  // Memory size (8GB)
)
if err != nil {
    return err
}

// Configure network
natAttachment, _ := vz.NewNATNetworkDeviceAttachment()
netConfig, _ := vz.NewVirtioNetworkDeviceConfiguration(natAttachment)
config.SetNetworkDevicesVirtualMachineConfiguration([]*vz.VirtioNetworkDeviceConfiguration{netConfig})

// Validate before creating VM
valid, err := config.Validate()
if !valid {
    return err
}
```

